{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e4398681fe","title":"中央复西北局关于伊斯兰教徒“朝罕”问题","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08c44b7687","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":27,"articleId":"e4398681fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4e12ea0c43","type":"title","text":"中央复西北局关于伊斯兰教徒“朝罕”问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"a6ed28b9f0","type":"appellation","text":"西北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"b50826e789","type":"paragraph","text":"西北局统战部五月十二日电悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"c14d78794b","type":"paragraph","text":"伊斯兰教徒“朝罕”问题，如我们长期不允许，就会在这个问题上陷于被动。同意你们提出的主动地有计划、有控制地允许一部分人出去“朝罕”的办法，请你们先试办一次，以便取得经验。惟请注意下列各点。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"047867830d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）人数尽可能少一些。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"985de07435","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）反革命分子、嫌疑分子、旧军官及土改地区之地主、恶霸分子不要去。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"2f0ffeab93","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）每人所带费用，以够用为原则，过多的应加以适当的限制。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"b21f42fe31","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"46208c462e","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"8c3c678c57","type":"subtitle","text":"西北局统战部对要求“朝罕”人的意见","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"961f4c031b","type":"subtitle","text":"（1951年5月12日）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"5fff956f3c","type":"appellation","text":"中央统战部并转公安部：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"48163898f1","type":"paragraph","text":"关于“朝罕”我们研究有如下意见：我们认为现在要求“朝罕”的人，多为地主旧军人（有些群众亦请求去但为数很少），这些人“朝罕”可能作一些反宣传，也可能与逃亡匪首马步芳、马步青取上联系，这是不好的一面，但另一面他们亦可能透露一些真实情况，如民族平等、团结互助，信教自由，同时我们可借此对近东信伊斯兰教各国取得一些联系，便利今后国际统战工作。因此，我们意见：虽不鼓励大家去“朝罕”，但应主动有计划的控制，坚决要“朝罕”的人，甚至派隐蔽力量，随同一块，去宣传政府信教自由，民族平等各种政策，并了解情况，以便利今后工作，以上意见是否有当，望复。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"},{"id":"acff6fd416","type":"paragraph","text":" 西北局统战部","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe"}],"page":{"id":"cd552afd55","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e4398681fe","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}